data.description:
Charming and beautiful country home on 5 acres! Enjoy the convenience of living in town and the charm of being on a more secluded road. This 3 bedroom, 2 bath house boasts a HUGE living and dining space, a completely renovated kitchen, and much more. New floors and paint throughout. New roof in 2023. New AC in 2023. Home energy efficiency test completed in 2022. 

Over 1,800 square feet, on 5 acres… This won’t last long - request to tour it today!
